trailingComments.value:
*
         * Boundary of the Canvas in absolute browser window coordinates.
         *
         * ### Usage:
         *
         * ````javascript
         * var boundary = myScene.canvas.boundary;
         *
         * var xmin = boundary[0];
         * var ymin = boundary[1];
         * var width = boundary[2];
         * var height = boundary[3];
         * ````
         *
         * @property boundary
         * @type {Number[]}
         * @final

